---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.svelte'
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Peter Hou" description="About Peter Hou">
  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi, I'm <strong>Peter Hou</strong>. You found it!</p>
        <p>I'm so happy to have landed this version of my homepage in 2026 — the third major iteration since the first was born in 2017, with the second following in 2023. This is actually just one of the hobby projects I'm currently building, all at the same time, with the help of AI. It has never felt so good to be a builder — ideas become real so fast now, like magic.</p>
        <p>I currently live on Mercer Island, an island in Lake Washington just east of downtown Seattle.</p>
        <p>I travel whenever I get the chance — and that's quite a lot. I love losing myself in different cultures and chasing landscapes that take my breath away.</p>
        <p>I love sports — though I'm not a gym guy. I'd rather be out on the field, sweating it out, sprinting to score, leaping to defend, and making full use of my agility and mobility. I love the competition of strength and speed. My sport of choice shifts over the years. Basketball, badminton, ultimate frisbee, baseball, American football, and more — each has been my favorite at one point or another. These days I primarily play frisbee and flag football, and I have no idea when my focus will shift again.</p>
        <p>In 2025, I happened to try softball for the first time with some friends — and quickly developed an interest in the game. I started watching MLB, and got to see the Seattle Mariners go all the way to the ALCS for the first time since 2001.</p>
        <p>It was also in 2025 that I fell in love with the NFL. Earlier that year, I watched the Eagles' win over the Chiefs, who had just won two straight Super Bowls in 2023 and 2024. From there I followed most of the games from the start of the new season. The speed and strength, the strategy and physicality, the clash at the line of scrimmage, the beautiful connection between quarterback and receiver — every play pulled me deeper in. I only wish I'd gotten into this sport sooner. I feel so fortunate, as a new fan, to have watched the Seattle Seahawks' legendary run all season long and witnessed their big win in the Super Bowl.</p>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <div class="contact">
        <h2>Leave Me a Message</h2>
        <ContactForm client:load />
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .content {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .contact h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--nav-color);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
</style>
